# =============================================
# EXPLICITLY TRACKED (use `git add -f` if needed):
# =============================================
# training_pipeline/models/*.pth       — Trained model weights (via Git LFS)
# training_pipeline/results/           — Leaderboard, best_config
# training_pipeline/plots/             — Confusion matrices, learning curves
# training_pipeline/logs/              — Per-model test metrics JSON
# training_pipeline/splits/            — Reproducible train/val/test splits
